HEADWORD: Presential
<hw>Pre*sen"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>praesentialis</ets>.]</ety> <def>Implying actual presence; present,
immediate.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>God's mercy is made <qex>presential</qex> to us.</q> <rj><qau>Jer.
Taylor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Pre*sen"tial*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Presentiality</ent>⟦br⟧
